---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import CountdownTimer from '../components/CountdownTimer.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import NewsletterBanner from '../components/newsletter-banner.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE, VELOREVOLTE_APPLICATION_URL } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<header>
			<h1>Krewe de Vélorévolte</h1>
			<p>Ride! Revel! Rally!</p>
			<div class="button-container">
				<a class="btn-primary" target="_blank"href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf5YbVz6M4kxTwqSqTzIThkG7RFaCDuVYNLHTk5804mjU7ZWw/viewform">Apply to Join</a>
				<a class="btn-secondary" href="#mission">Our Mission</a>
			</div>
			<video autoplay muted loop>
				<source src="/assets/video/hero-video.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
				Your browser does not support the video tag.
			</video>
			<CountdownTimer />
		</header>

		
		<section id="about-section">
			<img src="/assets/BikesOnTheBrain.webp" alt="Bikes on the Brain" width="328" height="528"/>
			<div class="copy-container">
				<h2>Membership Open Now!</h2>
				<p>
					At Krewe de Vélorévolte, we celebrate the vibrant diversity of our members—their backgrounds, experiences, and identities. We’re more than just a krewe; we’re a community that fosters connection, creativity, and fosters change for better bicycle infrastructure. 
	
					Join us in building a movement—one ride, one parade, and one rally at a time!
	
					<br>
					<br>
	
					<a href="https://www.instagram.com/krewedevelorevolte/" target="_blank">Follow us on Instagram</a> for updates and events as  information becomes available. Laissez les bons temps rouler!
				</p>
				<div class="social-container">
					<a class="social-link" href="https://www.instagram.com/krewedevelorevolte/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><!--!Font Awesome Free v7.0.0 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free Copyright 2025 Fonticons, Inc.--><path d="M224.3 141a115 115 0 1 0 -.6 230 115 115 0 1 0 .6-230zm-.6 40.4a74.6 74.6 0 1 1 .6 149.2 74.6 74.6 0 1 1 -.6-149.2zm93.4-45.1a26.8 26.8 0 1 1 53.6 0 26.8 26.8 0 1 1 -53.6 0zm129.7 27.2c-1.7-35.9-9.9-67.7-36.2-93.9-26.2-26.2-58-34.4-93.9-36.2-37-2.1-147.9-2.1-184.9 0-35.8 1.7-67.6 9.9-93.9 36.1s-34.4 58-36.2 93.9c-2.1 37-2.1 147.9 0 184.9 1.7 35.9 9.9 67.7 36.2 93.9s58 34.4 93.9 36.2c37 2.1 147.9 2.1 184.9 0 35.9-1.7 67.7-9.9 93.9-36.2 26.2-26.2 34.4-58 36.2-93.9 2.1-37 2.1-147.8 0-184.8zM399 388c-7.8 19.6-22.9 34.7-42.6 42.6-29.5 11.7-99.5 9-132.1 9s-102.7 2.6-132.1-9c-19.6-7.8-34.7-22.9-42.6-42.6-11.7-29.5-9-99.5-9-132.1s-2.6-102.7 9-132.1c7.8-19.6 22.9-34.7 42.6-42.6 29.5-11.7 99.5-9 132.1-9s102.7-2.6 132.1 9c19.6 7.8 34.7 22.9 42.6 42.6 11.7 29.5 9 99.5 9 132.1s2.7 102.7-9 132.1z"/></svg>		</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="mission">
			<h2>Our Mission</h2>
			<p>
				Long hidden underground in a sleeper cell, Vélorévolte has risen to herald the age of the bicycle. For years, cicadas lie buried in silence, unseen and unheard. In New Orleans, they can remain beneath the soil for thirteen to seventeen years, biding their time, gathering strength, awaiting their moment. Then, suddenly, in an extraordinary event called an emergence, they rise. The ground hums, the air vibrates, and a chorus fills the city.
			</p>
			<p>
				Their message is Vélorévolte. We have been waiting, organizing, building beneath the surface. Now our time has come. We emerge to flood the streets with art, sound, color, and movement — heralding a city shaped for bicycles, safety, and freedom from car dependency.
			</p>
			<p>
				Our cicada song is unmistakable. It calls us to revolt. We rise from New Orleans' underground cycling culture into full visibility. We take the streets with our bicycles, our voices, our chants, and our vision for safe, connected infrastructure.
			</p>
			<p>
				The moment has arrived for us to rise together in collective force. Our chorus is deafening. We cannot be ignored. As cicadas endure by overwhelming predators with sheer volume, so Vélorévolte thrives by overwhelming the car-centric order with solidarity, visibility, and joy.
			</p>
			<p>
				Cicadas feed on roots, loosening them so the old may be uprooted. They remind us that cycles of change cannot be restrained. So too do we declare that bicycles are the future of New Orleans, and change is inevitable.
			</p>
			<p>
				We may have lived in shadow, but our emergence is here. The streets will resound with bells, chants, and laughter. A new age has begun — and we are here to sing its song.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Membership Options</h2>
			<div class="card-container">

				<div class="card">
					<h3>Parade Participant</h3>
					<p>
						Join us in bringing the spirit of Krewe de Vélorévolte to life! As a parade participant, you’ll have the opportunity to ride, dance, and showcase our krewe’s energy in parades during Carnival. You’ll also be a valued part of our broader community, with access to general membership activities.
						<br>
						<br>
						To be a parade participant, you must:
						<ul>
							<li>Share our passion for bicycling, creativity, and community</li>
							<li>Complete the application process</li>
							<li>Pay membership dues</li>
							<li>Attend at least 50% of costume and float builds</li>
							<li>Be a Louisiana resident</li>
							<li>Be 21 or older</li>
						</ul>
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="card">
					<h3>General Membership</h3>
					<p>
						Don’t want to parade during Carnival? No problem! As a general member of Krewe de Vélorévolte, you’ll be part of a vibrant community that celebrates cycling, creativity, and camaraderie. Join us for social gatherings like soirées, parties, our book club, movie nights, and other community events—all while supporting our Krewe and the larger bicycle movement in New Orleans.
						<br>
						<br>
						To be a general member, you must:
						<ul>
							<li>Complete the application process</li>
							<li>Pay membership dues</li>
							<li>Attend any required info sessions</li>
							<li>Be a Louisiana resident</li>
							<li>Be 21 or older</li>
						</ul>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="contact-us">
			<h2>Get in Touch!</h2>
			<p>We'd love to hear from you! If you're interested in joining the krewe, please fill out the <a href={VELOREVOLTE_APPLICATION_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">application form</a>.</p>
			<p>If you have questions, or just want to say hello, please fill out the form below.</p>
			<form name="contact" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field">
				<label class="hidden">
					Don’t fill this out if you’re human: <input name="bot-field" type="text" />
				</label>
				<label>First Name
					<input name="firstName" type="text" required></input>
				</label>
				<label>Last Name
					<input name="lastName" type="text" required></input>
				</label>
				<label class="full-row">Email
					<input name="email" type="email" required></input>
				</label>
				<label class="checkbox-label full-row">Join our email list for news and updates
					<input name="subscribeToUpdates" type="checkbox"></input>
				</label>
				<label class="full-row">Subject
					<input name="subject" type="text" required></input>
				</label>
				<label class="full-row">Message
					<textarea name="message" required></textarea>
				</label>
				<button type="submit" class="btn-primary">Submit</button>
			</form>
		</section>

		<Footer />
		<NewsletterBanner />
	</body>
</html>

<style lang="scss">
@use '../styles/mixins.scss' as *;

	header {
		position: relative;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		justify-self: center;
		text-align: center;
		overflow: hidden;
		padding: 4rem 0 5rem 0;
		margin-top: 4rem;
		@include globalPadding;
		h1 {
			margin: 0;
		}
		p {
			font-size: 2.3rem;
			margin-top: 1rem;
		}
		video {
			width: 100%;
			height: auto;
			position: absolute;
			inset: 0;
			z-index: -100;
		}
		&::before {
			content: '';
			position: absolute;
			width: 100%;
			height: 100%;
			inset: 0;
			background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
			z-index: -10;
		}
	}

	.button-container {
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			justify-content: center;
			gap: 1rem;
			margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		}

		section {
			padding-top: 2rem;
			padding-bottom: 4rem;
			scroll-margin: 5rem;
			@include globalPadding;
			h2 {
				padding-top: 1.5rem;
				text-align: center;
			}
		}

		section:nth-of-type(2) {
			background-color: var(--color-black-light);
		}

		#about-section {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
			gap: 4rem;
			padding-top: 5rem;
			h2 {
				padding-top: 0;
			}
			img {
				width: 100%;
				height: auto;
			}
			.social-link {
				width: 1.75rem;
				display: inline-flex;
				padding: 0.75rem;
				background: var(--color-black-lighter);
				border-radius: 2rem;
				transition: all 0.2s ease;
				&:hover {
					background: var(--color-primary);
					transition: all 0.2s ease;
				}
			}
			svg {
				height: auto;
				width: 100%;
				fill: var(--color-white);
			}
		}

		#mission {
			h2 {
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}
			p {
				text-align: center;
			}
			ul {
				padding-left: 0;
			}
			li {
				margin: 2.5rem 0;
				list-style: none;
			}
		}

		.card-container {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
			gap: 3rem;
		}

		.card {
			background-color: var(--color-black);
			padding: 1.75rem;
			border: solid 1px grey;
			border-radius: 0.5rem;
			h3 {
				margin-top: 0;
				margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
				text-align: center;
			}
		}

		#contact-us {
			padding-top: 0;

			h2 {
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}
		}

		@include tabletDown {
			header {
				video {
					height: 100%;
					width: auto;
				}
			}
			.card-container {
				grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			}
		}

		@include mobileOnly {
			header {
				.button-container {
					flex-direction: column;
					width: 100%;
					a {
						width: 100%;
					}
				}
			}
			#about-section {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column-reverse;
				gap: 2rem;
			}
			.card {
				padding: 1rem;
			}
		}

</style>
